Constructor sets up the input values for placing an order.

Parameters:
authToken - the authorization token for the session with OptionsHouse
accountId - the account id under which the order will be placed
symbol - the security symbol (stock or option) of this order
quantity - the quantity of this order
limitPrice - the limit price of this order
side - the side of the order (buy or sell)
positionType - the position type of the order (open or close)
tif - the time-in-force of this order (Day or GTC or EXT)

quantity - the quantity of this order
limitPrice - the limit price of this order
side - the side of the order (buy or sell)
positionType - the position type of the order (open or close)
